data.description: Generation of k-cliques in a graph
data.PS: The following links are only valid for module list maintainers:
data.rationale:
This module attempt to complement to what is missing in Graph
    module by Jarkko Hietenami. Graph::Clique module is useful when one
    wants to generate list of cliques, given graph edges. Possible
    application of k-clique finding is classification, bioinformatics
    and many more.
